<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;2020愿望达成清单（摘自本页讨论区）</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;全部都是个人的小愿望，但是一想到就会很开心</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>排名不分先后，想到啥写啥。</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>补完Soulless的所有作品：</strong><a href="/i-thought-you-would-leave-even-the-reaper-for-me">我所希冀的一切；我所应得的一切</a>，<a href="/doctor-s-s-personnel-file">S███████博士的人事档案</a>，<a href="/the-special-bond-between-child-and-mother">母子情深，血浓于水</a>，<a href="/the-slow-asphyxiation-of-undiluted-ardor">溺爱窒息</a>，<a href="/scp-2707">SCP-2707</a>（格式随笔在翻（咕）了在翻了）</li>
<li><strong>翻一篇J文档：</strong><a href="/henzoid-crocket-s-proposal-j">Henzoid-Crocket的提案</a>（这是第一篇，之后还有<a href="/scp-tldr-j">SCP-太长不看-J</a>，<a href="/scp-cc-by-sa-3-0-co">SCP-CC BY-SA 3.0-CO</a>和<a href="/scp-pu1p-j">SCP-PU1P-J</a>）</li>
<li><strong>翻一篇正式文档：</strong><a href="/scp-4964">SCP-4964</a></li>
<li><strong>翻一篇2016愚人节文：</strong><a href="/sophia-light-at-the-end-of-the-tunnel">隧道尽头的Sophia Light</a>（后来还有<a href="/troy-lament-and-the-terror-ferrets-of-darkling-lane">Troy Lament和黑暗巷的恐怖雪貂</a>）</li>
<li><strong>时隔多年给原作者带来了+9的增分：</strong><a href="/reboot-or-how-i-learned-to-stop-worrying-and-love-the-apocal">重启或：我如何学会停止担忧并爱上世界末日</a><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-3')">3</a></sup></li>
<li><strong>翻一个中心页：</strong><a href="/mtf-psi-7-home-improvement-hub">机动特遣队Psi-7（“Home Improvement”-家居装饰）中心</a></li>
<li><strong>翻一篇CP（同人配对意味）文：</strong><a href="/i-thought-you-would-leave-even-the-reaper-for-me">我所希冀的一切；我所应得的一切</a>，<a href="/sophia-light-at-the-end-of-the-tunnel">隧道尽头的Sophia Light</a>，<a href="/stop-picking-on-me">傻屌丘比特：别再找茬了</a>其实都是（。（剩下的就都是意外了）</li>
<li><strong>离原文发布时间最近的翻译：</strong><a href="/flos">Flos</a>（原文6:11发布，翻译11:30发布）
<ul>
<li>记录更新：<a href="/awakening">觉醒之时</a> - 原文14:14发布，翻译18:53发布</li>
<li>记录再次更新：<a href="/finding-asmodeus-hub">寻找阿斯蒙蒂斯</a> - 原文11:38发布，翻译12:02发布（好了这个记录打不破了）</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>翻一篇meta文：</strong><a href="/scp-5309">SCP-5309</a></li>
<li><strong>翻一篇仙人掌的文：</strong><a href="/conviction">罪恶信念</a>（虽然这是他重写的，而且渺小到没进作者页，但它的第一稿似乎是TroyL写的，这么想好像更开心了（？）</li>
<li><strong>翻一篇Crossover文，双厨狂喜的那种：</strong><a href="/the-hitchhiker-s-guide-to-the-library">图书馆搭车客指南</a></li>
<li><strong>翻一篇重生计划设定的文：</strong><a href="/four-stories-told-in-order">按顺序讲四个故事来哄骗一只对私人问题过分好奇的有智能的断手</a>（虽然很勉强但有标签我就很开心了）</li>
<li><strong>翻一篇观谬格式文：</strong><a href="/slice-of-forum-life">论坛生活片段</a></li>
<li><strong>翻一篇观谬格式的CP（Creepypasta意味）文：</strong><a href="/substation-9">九号变电所</a></li>
<li><strong>翻一个竞赛中心页：</strong><a href="/reimagining-contest">重新想象竞赛</a></li>
<li><strong>翻一篇艺作页：</strong><a href="/raddagher-s-toon-zone">Raddagher的卡通基地</a></li>
<li><strong>翻一篇解密：</strong><a href="/scpdeclassified:scp-5466">解密：SCP-5466 - 创作者之死</a></li>
<li><strong>承包一个中心所有的文：</strong><a href="/finding-asmodeus-hub">寻找阿斯蒙蒂斯</a></li>
</ul>
<p>下面这些稍微功利一点，而且不是个人私心小愿望而是意外惊喜，但是真的超级有成就感：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>翻两篇同月的精品文：</strong><a href="/scp-5309">SCP-5309</a>（2020年8月精品SCP），<a href="/substation-9">九号变电所</a>（2020年8月精品故事）（这个月我开心死了）</li>
<li><strong>得到作者的致谢：</strong><a href="/scp-5096">SCP-5096</a>（在<a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/dianas-personnel-file">作者页</a>），<a href="/scp-5251">SCP-5251</a>（在<a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/forum/t-13660997/scp-5251#post-4753071">作者帖</a>），<a href="/scpdeclassified:scp-5466">解密：SCP-5466 - 创作者之死</a>（在<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/forum/t-13685431/scp5466-death-of-the-creator#post-4785122">讨论区</a>）</li>
</ul>
<p>今年数据：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>发布翻译</strong>：101</li>
<li><strong>发布SCP文档翻译：</strong>30</li>
<li><strong>发布故事翻译：</strong>45</li>
<li><strong>发布GoI格式翻译：</strong>2</li>
<li><strong>翻译过的作者数量：</strong>71</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<h1 id="toc1"><span>一点善意的行为。</span></h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">善良的人：</span></strong> <a href="/a-kind-of-christmas">这</a><a href="/scp-2331">不是</a>一篇条目。这是一个<a href="/the-melody-of-autumn-passing-into-winter">洞</a>，有谁在旅途中<a href="/reap-what-you-sew">穿过</a>此处，寻找足够让它们<a href="/scp-2772">爱</a>到终结的故事。<br />
<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/system:page-tags/tag/kindness#pages">它们的脚步还能被感觉到，印入纸页之中。</a><br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>——摘自<a href="/personnel-and-character-dossier">人员及角色档案</a></p>
</div>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="color: grey">我收集的Kind Man的出场文段。<br />
感觉现在补完翻译也不必要了全文校对也不必要了，就把它留在这里好了（。</span></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size:larger;">剧透注意。</span></strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;这个折叠页，按一下就是剧透</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;紫色香烟，蓝色墨水</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>按<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/system:page-tags/tag/kindness#pages">kindness tag</a>顺序排列：</p>
<ul>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>A Kind Of Christmas:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">In all instances where the SCP object has been capable of speech, the effector of the breach was described as “a kind man.”</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>From Unknown Admirer to Unknown Admiree:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Even if it's the kindest of men.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>&#8230;Like Clockwork:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">（其实我看了一遍原文但还是不敢确定）</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>Reap What You Sew:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">On the card, in a neat, blue, cursive script&#8230;The last thing Kairos saw before the lid shut and he was sent off to places unknown, was a loving smile, and a pair of kind eyes.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-1252:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">The letter had no return address and the message contained details of Suzie's condition written in neat blue ink. （蓝色墨水的neat，不过其实不加也可以？）</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-1353:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">I just woke up thinking about some man with kind eyes I saw down the street the day before, how he touched my arm and said he was sorry before walking off.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-1551:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Especially that man snooping around, the one with the kind smile.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-166:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">（<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">我暂时没找着，</span>不过我喜欢这个故事（。）我找到了！谁能想到会有空白折叠页这种操作啊！</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-1771:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Upon routine inspection of SCP-1771-03 during fall season, Agent ██ reported finding a letter directed to a non-existent inhabitant referred to only as 'the kind man who did the redecorating'.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-2331:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">I did something very kind for him once. We've had a kind of friendship ever since.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-2353:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Even that kind, poor fella cashiering the damn place was giving you a side-eye!</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-2442:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">You're kinder than the description frames you, you know.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-2552:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">I AM NO K[illegible].</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-2662:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Welcome Researcher K███ M██</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-2772:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">On the card was a note written with blue ink in neat cursive containing what is believed to be the entire decoded transcript of Auditory Event 482&#8230;</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-2882:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">'When Kindness Is Eclipsed With Cruelty'（大概是）</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-2909:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">One kind man had put a gun to me.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-2992:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Doctor K. M██(primary)</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-414:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Routine interviews will be conducted by Dr. K███ M██.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-5699:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">And even if, you would have still shown me kindness.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-5995:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">（别问，问就是没找着（。（我看了<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">一</span>两遍原文<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">两</span>三遍译文，<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">不过都没有特别仔细，就先这样吧</span>只发现了Agent Kevin McHannon（化名Keith McKinsey）和Kair Malone博士，但我觉得证据不足？？？</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-747:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Blue crayon written in neat cursive.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-797:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Dr.K███M██'s note（第二张图每次都把我吓一跳）</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>SCP-979:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">SCP-979 was featured in an exhibition by an artist under the pseudonym of The Kind Man, in the ████████ Museum.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>Seasick Sharks:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Even the strangers, that kind man who looked to me in pity as if he could know my sacrifice.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>The Melody Of Autumn, Passing Into Winter:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">the scarecrow and his kind friend had their discussion&#8230; His friend was there, sitting in the fog, exhaling a familiar purple smoke.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>The Slow Asphyxiation Of Undiluted Ardor:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">Once, a Kinder person arrived in the lizard's room of love.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>The Special Bond Between Child and Mother:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">even if it is to deliver to a world without Kind Men</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>They Who Find Darkness Loving:</strong></span> <span style="color: white">In that dream a man leans against a white hallway, puffing on a cigarette that produces purple smoke.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #a18cd1"><strong>This Is How We Build Revelation:</strong></span> <span style="color: #1e90ff">The bus driver announced no stops on her way home, kindly silent, and allowed her the space to ponder the difference between migration and abandonment.</span></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<h1 id="toc2"><span>一千道未愈的伤。</span></h1>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/local--files/lyricslinn-s-personnel-file/Avery%20Solace.jpg" style="width: 800px" class="enlarge" alt="Avery%20Solace.jpg" /><br />
<strong><span style="font-size:larger;">是来自<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3935168&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609816203" alt="Lyrics Linn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3935168)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;">Lyrics Linn</a></span>的<a href="/lyricslinn-s-calligraphy-notebook">神仙书法</a>！非常非常感谢(´∀｀)♡</span></strong><br />
<span style="color: grey">虽然我也不知道放在这里是不是特别合适，但既然这个tab就是个安利页就姑且先这样……</span>
<p><strong>然后也许有人愿意点一下<a href="http://czyesperanza.wikidot.com/all-about-avery-solace">这个链接</a>？</strong></p>
</div>
<div class="blockquote">
<p>Avery Solace博士进入它们的房间，换下衣服，假装没有注意到在它们无光的房间中央那儿，那个被漆黑粘液覆盖的人形。</p>
<p>该实体只会在心理学家开始爬上床后，才会开始说话。 Lament的声音变得同他腐坏的肉体一样泥泞，在看不见的墙壁间回响着。</p>
<p><em>“Avery，今晚又不吃药？你一定喜欢我在你身边吧。真希望其他医生不会嫉妒（get jelly）。”</em><br />
<span style="color: white"><tt>Avery在第二天早餐时才明白这个笑话。</tt></span><br />
“……我没那么糟。不论如何我是他们唯一的测试对象。我不是一只实验老鼠……药物没法让你离开，所以说它不起作用。”</p>
<p><em>“好吧，也不能说你不是只小白鼠。”</em><br />
<span style="color: white"><tt>直到它们差点被百吉饼呛住才消停。</tt></span><br />
Solace博士背向声音的来处，试着睡一会。它们最后感觉到的事，是有人在帮他掖被子。<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>——《<a href="/they-who-find-darkness-loving">它们与黑暗相爱</a>》，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(637830); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609816203" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(637830); return false;">SoullessSingularity</a></span>/著，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gpxx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4478534); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4478534&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609816203" alt="GPXx" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4478534)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gpxx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4478534); return false;">GPXx</a></span>/译</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><span style="color: grey">出于某种原因我也<a href="http://czyesperanza.wikidot.com/they-who-find-darkness-loving">重译</a>了一下这篇，然后明显地发现水平是真的不够啊Orz</span></p>
<div class="blockquote">
<p>Avery Solace盯着ta手里的马尼拉纸质文件夹。被脓液覆盖的Lament特工把他的手臂搭在ta脖子上，越过ta的肩膀看着。自从上一次事故之后，Solace博士第一次感觉到自己被一个团队所需要。“最后的希望”——非常合适的名字。</p>
<p>在ta黑暗的房间里，Solace博士换下衣服，躺到床上，盯着天花板。在ta视线的角落，ta的幻觉坐在床边，看着ta试图入睡。</p>
<p><em>“又不吃药了，Avery？我真是受宠若惊。”</em>Lament特工的仿制品笑出声来，那声音好像什么柔软又蓬松的东西正在慢慢地死去。</p>
<p>Solace博士没有回答。Ta只是不安地沉思着。</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">第一段记忆像一道光芒穿越亿万星辰，</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">在ta的注视下燃烧殆尽。</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Avery是一个研究小组的一员，该小组负责测试不可转移的认知危害和无害的模因学之间的界限，做的通常是其他不那么秘密的实验室里为实习生准备的工作。这对他认知神经学的博士学位是一种浪费——但又有谁会拒绝研究如此边缘的学科的机会呢？</p>
<p>第一次收容失效的时候他正在输入数据。他的导师走了进来，对他大声喊叫——他不记得具体说了什么了。可他永远不会忘记那双眼睛：瞳孔放大，像碧玉环绕着深渊。</p>
<p>他记得一阵汹涌的喜悦，像发烧时模糊扭曲的梦。</p>
<p>Avery从他的幻梦中清醒过来，发现自己仍被导师凝视着。那双眼睛从他的手掌中盯着他。他不知道她剩余的部分发生了什么。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">第二段记忆从第一段中升起，像胆汁涌上喉咙，</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">不请自来。</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>他负责管理上一次事故后重组的队伍。奇怪的是，一个平凡的科学家组成的小组，怎么竟会像他们研究的异常一样固执。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">最后一段记忆依然疼痛。</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">如一千道未愈合的伤口。</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content"></div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>——《<a href="http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/soullesshuman">一人血书求作者更新</a><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-4" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-4')">4</a></sup>》，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(637830); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609816203" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(637830); return false;">SoullessSingularity</a></span>/著，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/esperanza-cai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4113182); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4113182&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609816203" alt="Esperanza_Cai" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4113182)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/esperanza-cai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4113182); return false;">Esperanza_Cai</a></span>/译</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="blockquote">
<p>“所以……呃，你说啥？”</p>
<p>Avery Solace博士并没有明确地在看着Magnus博士。如果ta在看的话，ta就会明白自己刚刚朝他扔了一个重磅炸弹。Ta有特殊的能力可以看穿别人。Magnus博士在一口水喝到一半的时候停下来提出了这个问题。这个时候，两位研究员正在Site 19的餐厅里吃早饭。</p>
<p>Solace博士点了点头，动作急促而不稳，更像是肌肉抽搐。“SCP-055。我知道那是什么。大概。”</p>
<p>Ta看着Magnus博士抓了抓他的脑袋，一头金发整齐地梳成马尾辫。有几缕头发从束发的皮筋里松脱出来，随即屈服于重力。差不多是早上九点钟，他的发型就已经开始凌乱了。Avery Solace博士也好不到哪里去，穿着一件亟需熨烫的实验服，不过ta从来就没有衣冠齐整过。至少ta今天费心穿上了相配的袜子。</p>
<p>Magus博士清了清嗓子。“那。呃。你介意告诉我它是什么吗？”</p>
<p>回应他的是一个缓慢、近乎困惑的眨眼。“嗯。”</p>
<p>“你是说，你不想告诉我？”</p>
<p>又一下急促，僵硬的点头。Solace博士又啜了一口咖啡，快速地瞥了一眼一个空荡的角落，然后轻轻地歪了歪头。Magnus转身顺着ta的视线看过去，什么也没有看到。这让他模糊地想到了自己家里的猫。他转回去看着他的同伴。“那你介意告诉我原因吗？”</p>
<p>“……不礼貌？”Avery又歪了歪头，舔了舔干裂的嘴唇，喝了一口咖啡。</p>
<p>“你是说你不确定是不是无礼吗？一点都不无礼，Avery。你能——你应该告诉我。现在就说。”较高的那个人的话变得快速、深沉，令人窒息，与其说是请求不如说更像强烈要求。</p>
<p>Solace沉默了一段时间。ta呆滞的目光紧张地停留在一个空荡的角落里，眉头皱起，好像被空气冒犯了。“不。我觉得我不会说。人们……人们花了很多心思去搞清楚。他们现在还在努力。我不想毁了他们的乐趣……”</p>
<p>有一米八几高的Magnus站了起来，抓住另一位研究员单薄的肩膀。他让ta面对自己。他强迫ta与他对视，目光凌厉，充满了野心与找到突破口的狂热决心。“不，你一定要告诉我。现在就说。”一只手靠近了Solace脆弱的脖子，很容易就能折断。</p>
<p>可他的手被小心而坚决地撬开了。Solace拿着他的空盘和咖啡杯站了起来。“……不，那样会很没礼貌。我不想做无礼的事情，Magnus博士。明天见。”</p>
<p>要不是会违反人力资源规定，Magnus可能已经揍了ta一顿。<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>——《<a href="http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/soulless-sandbox-part-iii">一人血书求作者更新·第二季</a><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-5" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-5')">5</a></sup>》，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(637830); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609816203" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(637830); return false;">SoullessSingularity</a></span>/著，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/esperanza-cai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4113182); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4113182&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609816203" alt="Esperanza_Cai" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4113182)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/esperanza-cai" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4113182); return false;">Esperanza_Cai</a></span>/译</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="footnotes-footer">
